    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=d8p41e1zjl]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=d8p41e1zjl]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754101533&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=362\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599425025/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754101533&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"611\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599425040\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599425025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"da09d8be-e8cb-435e-bd48-5afd783fce5b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754101533&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=611 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754101533&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=362 1x\" /></span><p>Welcome to RenderMan Fundamentals, the official introductory training for Pixar's flagship renderer.</p><p>This page contains everything you need to install and learn the basics of RenderMan.</p><hr /><div class=\"expand-container conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-macro-id=\"ae0404ef-8712-41dc-ba22-690d5f245dd0\" data-macro-name=\"expand\" id=\"expander-236402204\"><div id=\"expander-control-236402204\" class=\"expand-control\"><span class=\"expand-control-icon icon\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"expand-control-text\">OCIO - ACES</span></div><div id=\"expander-content-236402204\" class=\"expand-content expand-hidden\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"70d3142d-12d3-4b73-bce4-e7b8d76dff05\" data-macro-id=\"6e5ac09554ee71c98f7526c00fe73e4a60198e2bbcdaa389a22695451db09635\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/568465504\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p>Jump in and explore the basics of the Aces color management suite in RenderMan, and what makes OpenColorIO the new industry color standard.</p></div></div><div class=\"expand-container conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-macro-id=\"8cac5bd9-3a70-4074-952e-89073b81b930\" data-macro-name=\"expand\" id=\"expander-237183405\"><div id=\"expander-control-237183405\" class=\"expand-control\"><span class=\"expand-control-icon icon\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"expand-control-text\">ACES Color Management</span></div><div id=\"expander-content-237183405\" class=\"expand-content expand-hidden\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"c3bbb305-0279-45d8-bbcc-05bd858fb5e2\" data-macro-id=\"1ac0807bef511b3b5a39aa8e1f43ebc22a753f77726c8bdc14bb620daba3824d\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/470507417\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p>OpenColorIO and the ACES color space are cutting-edge standards for improving every artist&rsquo;s creative toolset. This lesson demonstrates the visual benefits of ACES and shows you how to get setup and rendering with ACEScg in RenderMan.</p></div></div><p /><hr /><h3 id=\"R.F.-ColorManagement-NextSteps\"><span data-colorid=\"d8p41e1zjl\">Next Steps</span></h3><p>Ready for the next step in your RenderMan Fundamentals learning path?</p><p>Let&rsquo;s move on to learning the beautiful shaders that ship with RenderMan and are used by Pixar Animation Studios themselves.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/599228438\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"previousLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754380316&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599425025/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754380316&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599097429\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"previousLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599425025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"b8bd9f33-23be-4f05-80fc-763f5b46d004\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754380316&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=67 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754380316&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599523329/R.F.+-+Materials+-+PxrSurface\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599523329\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"nextLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599425025/nextLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757754388089&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599425025/nextLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757754388089&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599425037\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"nextLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599425025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"d41a2cfb-6fe4-48f7-98a5-899b